{"product_id":"grace-eyeshadow","title":"Grace Eyeshadow","description":"\u003ch5\u003e\u003cem\u003eDescription\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/h5\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003eBrand Seen In: ELLE, Vogue, InStyle, Marie Claire \u0026amp; More\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align: center;\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\"Kjaer Weis will change how you think about organic makeup\" - InStyle Magazine \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA luscious, light mocha color with a semi-matte finish.  \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"\u003eLeaves a subtle, natural looking sheen.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"\u003eKjaer Weis uses bamboo in our formula to achieve a smooth, silky finish.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"\u003eProduced in Italy\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"\u003eCCPB Certified Organic\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"\u003eNO artificial ingredients, such as petroleum, parabens, artificial coloring and fragrance, petrochemical emulsifiers.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"\u003eNOT tested on animals\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan style=\"line-height: 1.5;\"\u003eGluten FREE \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv style=\"text-align: left;\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e“As a makeup artist, this is a color I reach for again and again. I recommend it for its versatility and wearability.” – Kirsten Kjaer Weis Founder \u0026amp; Makeup Artist\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eOur Beauty Notes: \u003c\/em\u003eEspecially beautiful for everyday wear in the eyelid crease. \u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch5\u003e\u003cem\u003eUse\u00