r products are produced. This Italian inspection agency has some of the strictest standards for organic and natural certification in all of Europe. The CCPB approves the talc that we use in our products since it is the purest form of the ingredient and contains absolutely no asbestos. The talc we use is the complete opposite of those low-quality (conventional) loose powders. \u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Kjaer Weis","offers":[{"title":"Grace","offer_id":3706397636,"sku":"LB-KW-ESGRACE","price":45.0,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true},{"title":"Refill (Grace)","offer_id":6320592644,"sku":"LB-KW-ESGRACERF","price":27.0,"currency_code":"USD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0731\/0835\/products\/Copy_Eye_Shadow_Grace.jpg?v=1437504978","url":"https:\/\/levertbeauty.com\/products\/grace-eyeshadow","provider":"LeVert Beauty","version":"1.0","type":"link"}